  username VARCHAR(50),
  activity_type VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  details TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE user_interaction (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  interaction_details TEXT,
  interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE compliance_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  event_type VARCHAR(50),
  event_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  compliance_details TEXT
)

### STATEMENT

SELECT user_id, interaction_type, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM user_interaction GROUP BY user_id, interaction_type ORDER BY user_id, total_interactions DESC;
